description:
The Rawlings Heart of the Hide Bluefin 13" First Base Glove is a showstopper on the diamond, built for serious first basemen who want elite performance with next-level style. This exclusive design, only available at Better Baseball, features a stunning blonde, royal, and sky blue colorway with a unique topography-stamped leather design that turns heads. Crafted from the trusted Rawlings Heart of the Hide leather, this glove delivers unmatched durability and feel. The Rawlings 13" First Base Glove is built on the classic DCT pattern with a standard pocket depth and a reliable single-post web, perfect for scooping low throws and making big-time plays. Inside, you'll find a plush deer-tanned cowhide plus lining, a padded thumb sleeve for all-day comfort, and thermoformed wrist padding for snug, supportive fit. Whether you're flashing the leather or locking down the corner, this Heart of the Hide First Base Glove brings big league vibes and bold personality to your game. If you're searching for a standout Rawlings First Base Glove, look no further—this one is in a league of its own. function positionHandler() {
